<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Error Page</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6a11cb, #2575fc);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .error-container {
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            max-width: 400px;
            width: 100%;
        }

        .error-container h1 {
            font-size: 48px;
            margin: 0;
            color: #fc4a1a;
        }

        .error-container h2 {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #333;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        .error-container p {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #666;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .error-container a {
            text-decoration: none;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #fc4a1a, #f7b733);
            color: #fff;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            display: inline-block;
            transition: background 0.3s ease;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        .error-container a + a {
            margin-left: 10px; /* Space between buttons */
        }

        .error-container a:hover {
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #f7b733, #fc4a1a);
        }

        .error-icon {
            font-size: 60px;
            color: #f7b733;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .error-container .info {
            color: #007bff; /* Your desired color */
           
             font-weight: bold; 
            }


    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="error-container">
        <div class="error-icon">⚠️</div>
        <h1>Error Page Admin</h1>
        <h2>Something went wrong</h2>
        <p>We encountered an error while processing your request. Please try again later or contact support if the issue persists.</p>
        
        <p class="info">If you already logged in, click .</p>
        <a href="/admin/admin-dashboard">Back to Dashboard</a>
        <p class="info">If you are not already logged in, click .</p>
        <a href="/admin/admin-login">Login</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
